betterquesting:10.desc:8:
With the Nano Forge built, we can upgrade our production of circuit boards using Silver Nanites. Due to the nature of the nanites however, you will need both new structure casings and a special §5Nanite Containment Bus§r.

For the structure casings, you find that using infinity as a frame and enriched holmium as the protection layer works well. It can be allowed to let through nanites to go into the printer base so that extra material can be directly removed instead of trying to go slower.

With this new upgrade you can finally use §bTier 2 recipes§r. Additionally, by placing extra nanites into the Nanite Containment Bus, you can boost your parallel amount by §2Amount^.75§r up to §2256§r parallels.

[note]P.S. For those who don't feel like doing math, that's §n1638§r nanites to reach the maximum parallel amount.[/note]
